nd fast rescue operations.\n\nI worked on the Fairline 65 from 2019 to 2020, where I gained extensive experience in the bays of Marmaris and Göcek. From 2020 to 2024, I served on the Ferretti 565 motor yacht, operating in the Göcek, Fethiye, and Antalya regions. Currently, in 2024, I am employed as a seafarer on the Azimut 55 Cosmos yacht in Bodrum, Yalıkavak"}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":470000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":470000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"EUR","price":850000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":850000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"April","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2024-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2024-04-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-04-30T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-04-30T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","subTotal":470000,"totalTax":94000,"total":564000,"lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","conditions":"per week","quantity":1,"unitPrice":470000,"amount":470000,"taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2}}],"charterFee":470000,"unit":"WEEK"},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Turkey","type":"Sovereign country","category":["Asia","Western Asia","Turkey"],"coordinates":[35.10531997715448,39.093802942376584],"bbox":[25.6689453125,35.831445312499994,44.81718750000002,42.09326171875]}],"exclusionZones":[]},{"name":"October","effectiveDates":[{"from":"2024-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2024-10-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2025-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2025-10-31T23:59:59.999Z"},{"from":"2026-10-01T00:00:00.000Z","to":"2026-10-31T23:59:59.999Z"}],"pricing":{"currency":"EUR","inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","subTotal":525000,"totalTax":105000,"total":630000,"lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","conditions":"per week","quantity":1,"unitPrice":525000,"amount":525000,"taxRate":{"label":"VAT","value":0.2}}],"charterFee":525000,"unit":"WEEK"},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"Turkey","type":"Sovereign country","ca